<paragraph pageId="14" pageNumber="103">Culture characteristics.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="14" pageNumber="103">On PDA, cultures are initially white, becoming greyish-sepia after 3 d and distensible radially after 10 d. The colonies are felty with an irregular edge; texture uniform; sterile.</paragraph>
